<div id="body-special">
    <div class="summary">
        <img src="{{Content.Poster}}" width="360" height="200">
        <div class="txt">简介：{{Content.Summary}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="box">
        <h2>
            <span>专辑内容</span>
        </h2>
        <ul class="list">
            {{#each Content.Series.Programs.Program}}
                <li>
                    {{#contentType ContentType}}
                        <a href="program.html?id={{ContentID}}"><img src="{{Poster}}" height="80" width="100%"></a>
                    {{else}}
                        <a href="special.html?id={{ContentID}}"><img src="{{Poster}}" height="80" width="100%"></a>
                    {{/contentType}}
                    <h3>{{Name}}</h3>
                    <h4>这部动画片讲述的是对《星球大战》的故事发展极具关键性的克隆战争，这场战争导致内战时期开始，揭开《星球大战》的序幕。</h4>
                </li>
            {{/each}}
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
